{
  "stem": "19807.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 122.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then-- then after that, they began to come with cars.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One of my-- my mother's cousins was the first one to have a car, actually chauffeur-driven car, because they were representative of a very large German-American company.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So, primarily, was-- was horse-drawn carriage, buses, [DRINKS] and some cars.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was in the city.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But otherwise, trains.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, that was a ritual.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My father knew the train schedules.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The train, the smallest part, if you had to go from here to-- to the smallest village, it was by train.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They had a very good train system there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, let me just give you a little example of the street in which we lived, after we moved from original and we moved into the second dwelling, which in which I grew up for the following seven years.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The landlady was Bulgarian, the landlords.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I played with their son.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they had a son and-- my age and two, two daughters.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Underneath us there were Armenians.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I played with their kids.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In fact, they were very helpful in raising me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Across the street, there were Turkish people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I played with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they were Bulgarian, Turkish, Jews, and Armenians.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The first sign of anti-Semitism was in the neighborhood, when somebody began to call me, like, a dirty Jew.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I was in shock.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Why is it-- I did hear from my father, there were some displays of anti-Semitism in his-- in his work.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But he was so tough that he always was able to handle himself with that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But it was not anything prevalent.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "However, as the Nazis begin to advance and the fascist government-- government came, you could begin to see the signs.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
